{"tid":489313,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[運動錶撚]過二千字長文 SUUNTO ＆ GARMIN 多角度使用體驗","createTime":"2017-12-04T14:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T01:32:02.000Z","uid":25250,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"97acb88381c703392e211abb5e72f3137afbe406","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/201234_8d92ead2397ede3f189cb0ff0bc7f742.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F201234_8d92ead2397ede3f189cb0ff0bc7f742.jpg&h=e1072eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是次使用手錶<br />\nsuunto spartan sport wrist hr (推出年份2017）（賺入自美國amazon）<br />\ngarmin vivosmart hr+(推出年份2016)（台灣行貨）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://andrewskurka.korndev-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/suunto-spartan-sport-wrist-hr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fandrewskurka.korndev-cdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsuunto-spartan-sport-wrist-hr.png&h=10c0dc5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.garmin.com/en/products/010-01955-36/g/img-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.garmin.com%2Fen%2Fproducts%2F010-01955-36%2Fg%2Fimg-01.jpg&h=e2b9f457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等陣！你話我拎SUUNTO隻次旗艦錶對GARMIN既次中級錶比較<br />\n係啊，價錢同功能有差別（soprt wrist hr使用的是GPS＋GLONASS，vivosmart hr+只有單GPS，定位能力有極端差異）<br />\n所以我比較既係兩間廠既使用體驗，大家既優缺點囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nfitbit同iwatch？邊有咁多錢買曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">產地</span>：<br />\nSUUNTO:芬蘭<br />\nGARMIN:美國（台灣行貨則台灣製造）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">外型</span>：<br />\n<br />\nSUUNTO錶帶格數較多，合適不用手腕粗幼的人仕配戴，拉到最盡小學生既水都戴到，但係因為螢幕太大，會顯得手幼既人襯得唔好睇。夕膠比較硬，每次較格數都有d難，但係SUUNTO通常有兩個套套返實多出黎既錶帶。<br />\n<br />\nGARMIN錶帶較數比SUUNTO少，但係已經比一般手錶格數多，夕膠比較軟，調較時比較舒服，但係我自己隻HR+就用左唔夠1年，套住錶帶個膠套爛左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">語言</span>：<br />\n<br />\nSUUNTO:系統有多國語言設定，甚至有簡中，但係<strong>無繁中</strong>，字體庫都無香港字<br />\n「咁、喎」既字體會變成「龠」呢個字<br />\n而APP既語音就同裝置一樣咁多（廿幾種）但都係無繁中（屌）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGARMIN有分美國同台灣版，美國版無中文系統同中文字體，所以想係手錶睇到中文既短訊一定要買台灣版本，而台灣版本價錢就比美國版本貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過GARMIN既APP可以選繁中，如果怕手錶買完唔識用或者睇返D數據，個APP會幫到你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/210018_c5d4bd34560a2321b0847c8200a6a38e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F210018_c5d4bd34560a2321b0847c8200a6a38e.jpg&h=0065598f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">APP</span>：<br />\n<br />\n兩者個APP都免費係and同ios免費DL到，而且唔需要有裝置，單純用直接輸入數據都玩得<br />\n<br />\nSuunto Movescount：呢個垃圾爛鬼無撚用（難用資訊少）既APP，主要用途：<br />\n龜速同步裝置，睇返GPS地圖路線，過去30日運動 距離 心率 的平均數，心跳／跑速圖表<br />\n裝置睇唔到而APP睇到既數據少之又少 我自己搵到只有epoc（運動後過量氧耗）同無鬼用既影片模式之外，基本上裝置可以睇曬<br />\n仆你個街，每公里時間都無得睇，連換個儀表版都要經個APP駁上佢官網整，食屎啦芬蘭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGarmin Connect：每月更新，介面潮、易用，可以設定既功能都好多，要令GARMIN運動錶發揮到極致就一定要禁入個APP玩<br />\n自設訓練目標，最近睡眠質素，附近運動路線，卡路里消耗等等，唯獨是呢個APP功能多到我數唔曬所以割愛<br />\n注意返同裝置同步時雖然好快但係需要電話連到上網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">心率</span>：<br />\n<br />\nspartan sport wrist hr 係SUUNTO暫時唯一用光學測到心率既運動錶<br />\n除左運動同睡覺時（需要設定）外，平時都會處埋靜止模式唔會主動測量用家心率<br />\n而每次禁入去測心率，都需要等大約廿秒，偶爾需要調較位置先測量得到<br />\n冬天血管收縮時需要既時間都會耐D<br />\n雖然好似講到好多缺點，但係根據我以前入GYM房做運動既經驗，我自己覺得幾準<br />\n<br />\nGARMIN：家明既裝置基本上係全天侯偵測用家心跳，除左現時心跳之外，會額外提供一個叫「靜止平均心率」，可以簡單比較到最近心跳既情況，keep住做帶氧個期見到個數不停跌會幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於準確性方面，GARMIN會偶然跳動得比較勁，特別係調較完隻錶既位置之後，穩定性比SUUNTO差D，但都有一定既參考性<br />\n比較問題係佢成日測高導致卡路里個度高得好異常，每日消3000大卡是家明的常識吧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/214256_3c9125e09127c35c7e92990ea7cbfd32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F214256_3c9125e09127c35c7e92990ea7cbfd32.jpg&h=9589630c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">螢幕</span><br />\n<br />\nSUUNTO:可較調亮度比較多，而且製品通常係全螢幕，唔會留邊，就算因為手濕touch唔到mon，仲有3粒輔助制可用<br />\n<br />\ngarmin：買之前留意返係咪「全螢幕」 GARMIN有裝置係圓型錶面但係非成個員都顯示到，個顯示器可能只係長方型，我自己覺得家明掃mon個準確性高d<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">設定自由度：</span><br />\n<br />\nSUUNTO：用家得錶面款式，顏色同運動時儀表版可以設定，想玩多D野都唔得<br />\n<br />\nGARMIN:自由度極大，預設功能都比較多（比suunto多音樂，訊息等）貴價款仲可以上家明既市場下載小APP同唔同面版，日日幫隻錶換款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係平價走裝置就無得用家明市場啦，買之前記得google下"},{"pid":"84959043bf16d85ce56b9767fe875df2e0474755","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">訊息</span>：<br />\n<br />\nSUUNTO：同步速度快：顯示時間適中，加上支援多國語言彈出黎既訊息基本上都顯示到（除左香港字），但係蘇州過後無船搭，當你睇唔到信息彈出黎個幾秒，就一定要開電話睇返<br />\n<br />\nGARMIN：同步速度快：顯示時間適中，睇唔到可以自己掃去訊息個頁再慢慢睇，扮工一流，但係偶爾裝置同電話藍芽斷線時就無用<br />\n記得，要睇中文同香港字就要買台版啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">睡眠：</span><br />\n<br />\nSUUNTO：設定完睡時間帶就會異常地準確，入睡時間差唔多過3分鐘，起身更加係完全準確<br />\n就算係床度典下典下或者玩平板佢都測到你入睡個下<br />\n不過無時定時間帶，訓晏覺既話佢就唔會計<br />\n訓覺時會測你心率同埋起過身既時間（屙夜尿），仲有一週平均時間<br />\n呢一點係我買左隻錶之外有D意外既驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n缺點係入左睡眠時間帶每次都要解鎖隻錶先用得<br />\n<br />\nGARMIN：當係玩具玩下都仲得，雖然有分深層睡眠同表層睡眠，但係連訓覺時間都測唔準就唔好講呢D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">計步器：</span><br />\n<br />\nSUUNTO：參考性低，當隻手揮大少少都計你一步，做藍領既我每日步數都被突破2萬步，最過份係入左睡眠模式翻身都計我行路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但係假日單純做運動個參考數就好正常<br />\n<br />\nGARMIN：參考性高，只要唔係過份大動作都會偵測到，同我電話既計步器差1成左右，而且根據過往既步數，每日都會自動調節目標，加上GARMIN有氣壓計可以計埋上落樓梯，但氣壓計參考性唔太高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">GPS比較：</span><br />\n自己google會見到台灣好多評測，所以我不了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">整體感想：</span><br />\n<br />\nSUUNTO:GPS真係好準，加上心率測量幾高參考性，如果對於自己運動有高要求既人會好合適，功能簡單易用<br />\n<br />\nGARMIN:功能多，玩樂性高，造型潮，如果偶然運動又唔鍾意iwatch既款式，garmin絕對係一個好選擇，但注意返GARMIN每款用既GPS都唔同<br />\n<br />\n打左好多字，好累"},{"pid":"960266ee25c91e8b83891b255cc30ab060746721","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fc6c0308225127136ed99de6ab908dce3c7242","tid":489313,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845708a0acba944b47aae5fd7752074cc0747e37","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cba871ca59d45098b24852edefdf6746f3bf70","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3e66d7f424fc5f1c9f65fe61a2726ddf56d159","tid":489313,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:24:32.000Z","msg":"睇完dc rainmaker嘅spartan sport評測<br />\n果斷入咗garmin  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a08eeb5ffffe9b6ed263e3b2d167b3e1bf4c693","tid":489313,"uid":4629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係amazon 買左隻vivosmart hr+ 等緊佢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da16a50259f95302676c312f373982014ee559f","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完dc rainmaker嘅spartan sport評測<br />\n果斷入咗garmin  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己同D FD用開中文溝通，無左中文顯示真係廢左半部機<br />\ngarmin d台機又貴到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afc98211446feaf0c366873f03c2500a83f5d95","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係amazon 買左隻vivosmart hr+ 等緊佢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢隻平靚好玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350a747b5c70e542159693296d4581ec3fd1b02b","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf337b3fe9959640057092df700b11bffdab31c","tid":489313,"uid":4629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"但係呢類光學check heart rate係咪如果心跳有大變 (啱啱開始/完運動，gym類）都會跟唔上/唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7af35ea1306bdcab4a66dc9177e7bc6ec7e739","tid":489313,"uid":42705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係呢類光學check heart rate係咪如果心跳有大變 (啱啱開始/完運動，gym類）都會跟唔上/唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，要準啲可以用心跳帶。不過誤差好似唔大得去邊。"},{"pid":"2c404f0e6ad6f1c6dacfdd5efb7c93868c912055","tid":489313,"uid":29134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路都想買suuto<br />\n睇完可以睇埋家明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6f33294b50b43e52231661982457bb934dcde5","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係呢類光學check heart rate係咪如果心跳有大變 (啱啱開始/完運動，gym類）都會跟唔上/唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，要準啲可以用心跳帶。不過誤差好似唔大得去邊。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/191933_d0d488f37290ff19ebfc54c9a67eae83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F191933_d0d488f37290ff19ebfc54c9a67eae83.jpg&h=ce527e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8分鐘個度會跌係因為等紅綠燈停左<br />\n雖然個偵察數上上落落無心跳帶咁平均<br />\n(因為漏斗胸用唔到心跳帶做唔到實測）<br />\n但係最大值同平均值對比gym房既數值差唔多<br />\n值得一提既係 suunto用既光學偵察零件比iwatch同garmin更準 但好食電"},{"pid":"9513e849f05630391579850b6dc38cc364c2b1d8","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/192455_6e00d30498a3e3182aabc3ccc3388ce5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F192455_6e00d30498a3e3182aabc3ccc3388ce5.jpg&h=2a05ddeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係我用garmin hr+既心跳數據<br />\n比suunto平穩"},{"pid":"427913450e460d8450d92fbee8b29483fb7bde66","tid":489313,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/192455_6e00d30498a3e3182aabc3ccc3388ce5.jpg[/mg]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F192455_6e00d30498a3e3182aabc3ccc3388ce5.jpg%5B%2Fmg%5D&d=15sorSp55q6zJ%2BKvq7GJ6Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f83889b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/192455_6e00d30498a3e3182aabc3ccc3388ce5.jpg[/mg]</a><br />\n呢個係我用garmin hr+既心跳數據<br />\n比suunto平穩</blockquote><b